::KitKat::

Despite the cold chill in the air, she felt high spirited.
She looked at Rowdy and then up at Terrorsaur. "Are we there yet?" 
with the voice of an impatient pup.  She smirked, "Then let's pick up 
the pace."  She sped off through the trees and ran as fast as she 
could.  She loved to run, as it was one of her true passions in 
life.  She weaved in and out of the trees. "Come on you slow pokes."
She said with a smirk on her face and the wind in her fur.
